description: A little beauty walked into my office this morning. Well dressed and with a cool hairstyle. According to his CV he worked at an insurance company before. Mainly paper-work. I was almost shocked to hear how bad those jobs are paid. He got only 15 000 CZK a month in that position. Afterwards he worked at a bar and even made a barman-certificate. Indeed one has to be flexible nowadays. We spoke a lot about his life and expenses. He was very open and talkative. And as he was applying for the warehouse-position I was only worried that he would maybe be to slim for this job. But he assured me that he is sportive and capable of hard work. So I told him about the 5 000 CZK one-time fee and also told him my offer to get naked instead. His reaction war amazing...
title: Dirty Scout 18
